ğŸ©º Project Overview

This project focuses on **analyzing patient data**, identifying clusters of patients with similar characteristics, and predicting the risk of disease. By combining **unsupervised learning** (clustering) and **supervised learning** (classification), healthcare professionals can better understand patient patterns and make informed decisions.

The system helps to:

* Segment patients into meaningful clusters.
* Predict the likelihood of disease for a new patient.
* Visualize patterns in patient demographics and medical features.

